  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6776.1 sitting just below the flip at 6783 and sandwiched between the massive +115B gamma wall at 6780 and -39B negative gamma at 6770, dealers are actively selling delta into any push toward 6780 while preparing to buy aggressively if we break 6770. The 24.8% and 63.6% GEX surge indicates fresh positioning has created a tight PIN regime with heavy stabilizing forces, making the 6770-6785 range a high-conviction mean reversion zone. Watch for dealer resistance to intensify as we approach 6780 (+115B gamma wall) and immediate buying support if 6770 breaks, which would trigger aggressive dealer covering into negative gamma territory.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect strong magnetic pull keeping price locked between 6770-6785 with quick reversals at the boundaries.",
